quran[6{c,v,t}:
8,70,ae paighambar jo qaidi tumahray haath mein ( girftar ) hain un se keh do ke agar khuda tumahray dilon mein neki maloom kere ga to jo ( maal ) tum se chhin gaya hai is se behtar tumhe inayat farmaiye ga aur tumahray gunah bhi maaf kar day ga aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
8,71,aur agar yeh log tum se dagha karna chahain ge to yeh pehlay hi khuda se dagha kar chukay hain to is ne un ko ( tumahray ) qabzay mein kar diya. aur khuda Dana hikmat wala hai
8,72,jo log imaan laaye aur watan se hijrat kar gay aur khuda ki raah mein apne maal aur jaan se larray woh aur jinhon ne ( hijrat karne walon ko ) jagah di aur un ki madad ki woh aapas mein aik dosray ke Rafeeq hain. aur jo log imaan to le aeye lekin hijrat nahi ki to jab taq woh hijrat nah karen tum ko un ki rafaqat se kuch sarokaar nahi. aur agar woh tum se deen ( ke mamlaat ) mein madad talab karen to tum ko madad karni lazim hogi. magar un logon ke muqablay mein ke tum mein aur un mein ( sulah ka ) ehad ho ( madad nahi karni chahiye ) aur khuda tumahray sab kamon ko dekh raha hai
8,73,aur jo log kafir hain ( woh bhi ) aik dosray ke Rafeeq hain. to ( momino ) agar tum yeh ( kaam ) nah karo ge to malik mein fitnah barpaa ho jaye ga aur bara fasaad mache ga
8,74,aur jo log imaan laaye aur watan se hijrat kar gay aur khuda ki raah mein laraiyan karte rahay aur jinhon ne ( hijrat karne walon ko ) jagah di aur un ki madad ki. yahi log sachey musalman hain. un ke liye ( khuda ke haan ) bakhshish aur izzat ki rozi hai
8,75,aur jo log baad mein imaan laaye aur watan se hijrat kargaye aur tumahray sath ho kar jehaad karte rahay woh bhi tum hi mein se hain. aur rishta daar khuda ke hukum ki ro se aik dosray ke ziyada haqdaar hain. kuch shak nahi ke khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
